[04/10/2018 02:55:06] <font color="#ffff00">Hola.</font>
[04/10/2018 02:55:06] <font color="#00ffff">Hola, Kevin. James.</font>
[04/10/2018 02:55:08] <font color="#ffff00">¿Qué tal? Encantado, Nicky.</font>
